                    <h3 class="p-work-overview--kamsa p-work-overview__title" id="the-challenge">The Challenge</h3>
                    <div class="p-work-overview__description"> The HR/People and Finance leaders responsible for
                      compensation management need a user-friendly platform that can
                      simplify the complex process of compensation management and make it easy to use. The existing UI
                      design of the Kamsa
                      platform was not meeting the needs of these users, leading to a suboptimal user experience and
                      inefficiencies in the
                      compensation management process.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
