                    <h3 class="p-work-overview--kamsa p-work-overview__title" id="the-solution">The Solution</h3>
                    <div class="p-work-overview__description">The solution to this problem was to revamp the User
                      Experience (UX) design of the Kamsa platform. The goal was to make
                      the platform visually appealing and user-friendly. This was achieved by creating wireframes based
                      on UX research
                      results, which served as the foundation for a new UI design for the entire platform. The project
                      concluded with the
                      development of a sophisticated design system for a seamless user experience. The result was that
                      Kamsa closed the gaps
                      in compensation, helping companies pay their employees competitively and leading to a happier,
                      more productive
                      workforce.
                    </div>
